    ('Kids',       'shop-kids',  'Safe, certified 925 silver jewellery designed for kids — lightweight, skin-friendly and adorable.', 'https://cdn.hadha.co/categories/shop-kids.jpg', 30, TRUE, 'Silver Jewellery for Kids | Hadha.co', 'Shop certified 925 silver jewellery for kids. Safe, lightweight and adorable designs at Hadha.co.')
