    ('HD-KPD-0002','Moon Star Pendant Kids','moon-star-pendant-kids','Dreamy crescent moon and star pendant for children in 925 sterling silver. The classic celestial combination is rendered in smooth polished silver. Perfect for little dreamers.','Dreamy 925 silver crescent moon and star pendant for kids. Smooth polished celestial design.','k-pendants','925 Silver','925','BIS925KPD002','4.0','110.00','4.0','kids','699','899','419','30','true','true','false','Moon Star Pendant Silver for Kids | Hadha.co','Shop moon star pendant for kids in 925 sterling silver. Classic celestial design for little dreamers.','moon star pendant, celestial pendant, kids pendant, 925 silver, children jewellery'),
    ('HD-KPD-0003','Heart Pendant Kids Silver','heart-pendant-kids-silver','Classic heart pendant for children in 925 sterling silver. The smooth polished heart has a small engraved star at the centre. A universal symbol of love for the people who matter most.','Classic 925 silver heart pendant with engraved star at centre. Symbol of love for children.','k-pendants','925 Silver','925','BIS925KPD003','2.0','75.00','3.0','kids','499','699','299','50','false','false','true','Heart Pendant Silver for Kids | Hadha.co','Buy heart pendant for kids in 925 sterling silver. Polished heart with engraved star — symbol of love.','heart pendant, kids pendant, 925 silver, love pendant, children jewellery'),
    ('HD-KPD-0004','Fish Pendant Kids Silver','fish-pendant-kids-silver','Lucky fish pendant for children in 925 sterling silver. The detailed fish has textured scales and a flared tail. Fish symbolise prosperity and good luck — a meaningful gift.','Lucky 925 silver fish pendant for kids with textured scales and flared tail. Symbol of prosperity.','k-pendants','925 Silver','925','BIS925KPD004','3.0','90.00','3.0','kids','599','799','359','28','false','true','false','Fish Pendant Silver for Kids | Hadha.co','Shop fish pendant for kids in 925 sterling silver. Lucky symbol of prosperity with detailed scales.','fish pendant, lucky pendant, kids pendant, 925 silver, prosperity jewellery'),
    ('HD-KPD-0005','Crown Pendant Kids Silver','crown-pendant-kids-silver','Royal crown pendant for children in 925 sterling silver with tiny enamel gems at each crown point. Every little girl is a princess — this pendant celebrates that spirit beautifully.','925 silver crown pendant for kids with enamel gems at each crown point. Every child is a princess.','k-pendants','925 Silver','925','BIS925KPD005','4.0','125.00','4.0','kids','799','999','479','22','false','false','false','Crown Pendant Silver for Kids | Hadha.co','Buy crown pendant for kids in 925 sterling silver. Enamel gems at crown points for little princesses.','crown pendant, princess pendant, kids pendant, 925 silver, girls jewellery'),
    -- KIDS GIFTS
    ('HD-KGF-0001','Baby Gift Jewellery Set','baby-gift-jewellery-set','Complete 925 silver jewellery gift set for babies, including a tiny bracelet, an anklet, and a chain with a heart pendant. Beautifully presented in a Hadha.co gift box — the perfect new baby gift.','Complete 925 silver baby set: bracelet, anklet and heart chain in Hadha.co gift box. Perfect new baby gift.','k-gifts','925 Silver','925','BIS925KGF001','12.0','280.00','5.0','kids','1499','1899','899','20','true','true','false','Baby Gift Jewellery Set Silver | Hadha.co','Buy baby jewellery gift set in 925 silver. Bracelet, anklet and heart chain in gift box — perfect baby gift.','baby gift set, newborn jewellery, 925 silver, baby gift, silver set, new baby'),
    ('HD-KGF-0002','Kids Birthday Gift Set','kids-birthday-gift-set','Cheerful birthday gift set for children in 925 sterling silver, including star stud earrings, a star bracelet, and a star pendant chain. Presented in a colourful birthday-themed gift box.','925 silver birthday gift set: star earrings, bracelet and pendant chain in birthday gift box.','k-gifts','925 Silver','925','BIS925KGF002','10.0','235.00','5.0','kids','1299','1699','779','18','false','false','true','Kids Birthday Gift Set Silver | Hadha.co','Shop kids birthday gift set in 925 sterling silver. Star earrings, bracelet and pendant in gift box.','kids birthday gift, silver gift set, children jewellery, 925 silver, birthday jewellery'),
    ('HD-KGF-0003','Kids Naming Ceremony Set','kids-naming-ceremony-set','Sacred 925 silver jewellery set for naming ceremonies, including a baby bracelet, anklet, and om pendant chain. A blessed beginning and timeless gift for newborns and their families.','925 silver namkaran set: bracelet, anklet and om pendant. A blessed beginning for the baby.','k-gifts','925 Silver','925','BIS925KGF003','15.0','365.00','5.0','kids','1999','2499','1199','10','true','true','false','Kids Naming Ceremony Jewellery Set | Hadha.co','Buy naming ceremony jewellery set in 925 silver. Bracelet, anklet and om pendant for namkaran.','naming ceremony set, namkaran jewellery, 925 silver, baby set, newborn jewellery'),
    ('HD-KGF-0004','Baby Shower Gift Set','baby-shower-gift-set','Thoughtful baby shower gift set in 925 sterling silver with a teddy bear pendant chain, a tiny bangle, and a pair of flower stud earrings. Comes in a deluxe baby shower gift box.','925 silver baby shower set: teddy pendant chain, tiny bangle and flower studs in deluxe gift box.','k-gifts','925 Silver','925','BIS925KGF004','14.0','330.00','5.0','kids','1799','2299','1079','14','false','false','false','Baby Shower Gift Set Silver | Hadha.co','Shop baby shower gift set in 925 silver. Teddy pendant, bangle and flower studs in deluxe gift box.','baby shower gift, silver baby set, 925 silver, baby jewellery, shower gift'),
    ('HD-KGF-0005','Kids Festival Gift Set','kids-festival-gift-set','Festive 925 silver jewellery set for children including a floral anklet, a butterfly chain, and a pair of flower stud earrings. Wrapped in a festive gift package — perfect for Diwali and Navratri.','925 silver festive kids set: floral anklet, butterfly chain and flower studs. Perfect for Diwali.','k-gifts','925 Silver','925','BIS925KGF005','12.0','290.00','5.0','kids','1599','1999','959','16','false','true','true','Kids Festival Gift Set Silver | Hadha.co','Buy kids festival gift set in 925 silver. Floral anklet, butterfly chain and flower studs for Diwali.','kids festival gift, diwali gift, navratri jewellery, 925 silver, kids set')
